title: Budget Impasse Begins to Affect Funding for 9-1-1 Centers (Aurora Regional Chamber of Commerce)
text: ( Source : Aurora Regional Chamber of Commerce ) On Monday, October 5 , St. Clair County announced that it had commenced litigation against the State of Illinois . At issue is money from a tax that Illinois extracts from the cellphone bills paid
